{"tid":62673,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"求收養（金青苔）","createTime":"2017-01-01T06:20:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-01T06:20:34.000Z","uid":71089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"088c5a85fff98d19d1c3afcbd6b9643f3f09d4dc","tid":62673,"uid":71089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T06:20:34.000Z","msg":"本身係條魚仔，宜家養大咗就霸山為王，日日嚇我啲神仙。唔知係咪個缸細又少草先會咁，求有能力人士收養。<br />\n唔係佢走就係神仙亡。<br />\n<br />\n7cm左右，非常之精靈古惑，一有人影就唔出現。我要離遠zoom埋去先影到，所以請原諒像素咁差。<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/9gup8weq\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F9gup8weq&h=8d6496e4&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}